    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-09-23T13:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-09-23T13:00:00-05:00" n="778"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d778">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/11434</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_SWG1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Sharp</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-09-23T14:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 23, 1918, 2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>5694. For Jassy:</p>
                <p>In reply to your joint telegram dated September 14, you may assure Roumanian
                    Government and people that purpose of the Government and people of the United
                    States has not been modified in any way and remains as expressed in message from
                    the President telegraphed to you November 1 [<hi rend="italic">28</hi>],
                        1917.<note n="1" xml:id="d778fn1">
                        <ref target="frus1917Supp02v01#pg_325">
                            <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1917, Supplement 2, vol. I, p.
                            325</ref>.</note> You may reiterate the sense of that message
                    emphatically.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
